song.title: Out Of The Dome [remix - instrumental version]
song.info:
this remix is made upon the sid which is a very short intro tune but i started building on the main part and this is came out. i don't think it's a remix as such it's more of a tune inspired by the sid and has some of the sid elements inside...
although this is the shortened instrumental version. the full vocal version will be available for slayradio listeners...
